Remotes: afsc-gap-products/akgfmaps
Description: This package calculates oceanographic data products for the eastern Bering Sea, northern Bering Sea, Gulf of Alaska, and Aleutian Islands using data from AFSC/RACE/GAP summer bottom trawl surveys. Products include temperature time series (e.g. mean bottom and surface temperatures, EBS cold pool index), temperature and salinity raster, oceanographic profiles from TDRs and CTDs, and plots.
